{"tid":149650,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"關島5天4夜包膠","createTime":"2017-03-09T12:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T07:43:48.000Z","uid":21992,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5e13f1619c60c15d39e4b99fb5e2209d530783a","tid":149650,"uid":21992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T12:20:57.000Z","msg":"之前開過一個關島post  打算向去過既巴絲取經 希望玩得抵d 平d 但可能關島比較冷門 同 上年先有hke 直航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以旅遊台未見有太多關於關島既旅遊資訊 有見及此 想試下寫個包膠 或者集合其他人既經驗 避免中伏 同 多d 好玩推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：第一次寫包膠 如有出錯 請指點<br />\n           多謝放平價機票比我個位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3d822b13b76dbd466f5551626b87a19e6b019b","tid":149650,"uid":21992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T12:27:04.000Z","msg":"主力玩跳傘 潛水 揸飛機 環島遊<br />\nDay1<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zze342L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZze342L.jpg&h=3ebd94cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搭hke 0930 出發 關島快兩個鐘 當地時間1700到達入境 但過關人多 排左成一個鐘先入到境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/09/202539_88b448b8ce8d6bb4c33cdfce572dd683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F09%2F202539_88b448b8ce8d6bb4c33cdfce572dd683.jpg&h=237cb6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1w3viun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1w3viun.jpg&h=83670c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到埗後 即刻去民宿放低d 行李 行左去海邊影下相 順便搵下有咩食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48d1055c2431cb6693d033e17e801f4de15bd95","tid":149650,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T12:28:46.000Z","msg":"隻機full唔full?