"msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Hi巴打記唔記得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪放飛比小弟個位巴打?</blockquote><br />\n係呀<br />\n<br />\n等遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5f52166286d0c0033546865b4960cc5916b37a","tid":149650,"uid":21992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T16:05:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Hi巴打記唔記得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪放飛比小弟個位巴打?</blockquote><br />\n係呀<br />\n<br />\n等遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝支持 你本身去過Guam?"},{"pid":"d7c779ee1f40f2485d5011aedb8f9e76a498f92c","tid":149650,"uid":21992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T16:30:19.000Z","msg":"Day2 上午跳傘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  下午揸飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日（風和）日麗 天氣唔錯 兩項兩活動都可以如期進行 首先就係朝早去跳傘 有專車接送服務 非常方便 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/000724_0f3564ea4fbe9571b1e79b7c058b9be1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F000724_0f3564ea4fbe9571b1e79b7c058b9be1.jpg&h=4cd57fc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/000726_fc8991b4f469340e81601c7094f4a68a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F000726_fc8991b4f469340e81601c7094f4a68a.jpg&h=5db1a21c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坐左大約半個鐘 就到左sky guam 既辦公室 兼 機庫 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/001906_3329fdf5a50e791b0d6e48d58959e478.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F001906_3329fdf5a50e791b0d6e48d58959e478.jpg&h=976c037c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入去之後 會先坐定定聽佢講解 生死狀點填 同埋有段跳傘教學需要睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/002108_3e8e80b0ef9480fcc6379f327e2180cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F002108_3e8e80b0ef9480fcc6379f327e2180cb.jpg&h=02065ac0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/002111_ef59bce9bcd89fcb4c4d48113b4bd381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F002111_ef59bce9bcd89fcb4c4d48113b4bd381.jpg&h=b7697d29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於全程係禁止拍攝 所以只能影到依到<br />\n簽好曬野 睇完段片 就可以著佢提供既藍色跳傘服 之後著好就入去配對一位教練 簡單吹兩嘴後 就準備上機 我玩既係10000ft  大概係雲層以上 再高少少 所以第一個跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/003009_4f8bbae34bf99402927901c241d9ac89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F003009_4f8bbae34bf99402927901c241d9ac89.jpg&h=85de2450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跳完之後 教練會比反張證書你 證明你玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e5d97d4a333e205eeb3a9c802c0b3e97bd9466","tid":149650,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T16:31:35.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"1f97e9ba84b53169e6aff802cea30c266a00fe66","tid":149650,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T16:48:32.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知物價"},{"pid":"b9f668e21f864b589b70fd9237e8a1a80eeac646","tid":149650,"uid":14595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T20:53:25.000Z","msg":"我都想去"},{"pid":"c387ae31b4a640891fa8250faedd30a220df538a","tid":149650,"uid":21992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T01:59:43.000Z","msg":"跳完傘會送我地反民宿附近既酒店<br />\n食左少少野 又準備出發 等揸飛機既人黎接<br />\n又坐左半