4c614d78bf818db23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F100459_f45a10b45d292494c614d78bf818db23.jpg&h=f2f27d78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9275b9cebba91b0943060b4b28b21fd35a87d1a1","tid":149650,"uid":21992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T02:11:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>琴晚正打算去 等樓主live</blockquote><br />\n揸飛機個人覺得有點貴 唔係咁值 上到空中 風好大 架飛機唔易操控 好多時都要教練控制 變左樂趣少左好多 不過個景又係好靚 教練會簡單講下 下面既地方係邊到 例如美軍基地 就可能只有空中先睇得到 地面好似係禁止進入"},{"pid":"b05a3a62f022dbdc69b5d5251ee431d9f258eda1","tid":149650,"uid":21992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T02:13:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>琴晚正打算去 等樓主live</blockquote><br />\n揸飛機個人覺得有點貴 唔係咁值 上到空中 風好大 架飛機唔易操控 好多時都要教練控制 變左樂趣少左好多 不過個景又係好靚 教練會簡單講下 下面既地方係邊到 例如美軍基地 就可能只有空中先睇得到 地面好似係禁止進入</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跳傘個人十分推薦 不過當然要量力而為 絕對係一個難忘既體驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484987cab07ea96cb86cc0d345d2d7e5e445105e","tid":149650,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T02:16:15.000Z","msg":"跳傘幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e36629c1dda547adc01e4f37804715a4b2d328","tid":149650,"uid":21992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T02:18:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知物價</blockquote><br />\n物價 可樂大約一支1-1.5usd <br />\n搭巴士 4usd 一程<br />\n食野 最平食過6usd（夜市$ 最貴暫時20usd （餐廳）"},{"pid":"00be9b31d64e502ec8da780efbd5eee59989c09d","tid":149650,"uid":21992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T02:24:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跳傘幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSorry  講少左 <br />\n8000 ft 289usd <br />\n10000ft 329usd<br />\n14000ft 429usd <br />\n愈高自由落體愈耐<br />\n價格只供參考 來自skydiving guam"},{"pid":"8c7a12da65516c07619401713b1d243207cfa522","tid":149650,"uid":21992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T02:50:40.000Z","msg":"Day2 晚餐 上午玩完跳傘 下午揸飛機<br />\n之後就因為民宿附近 無免費巴士 太唔方便 最後都係租左架車代步<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Pm98Rx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Pm98Rx.jpg&h=d7021f0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大約29usd per day （已包基本保險）想係機場拎車 還車要加20usd 另外其他保險要加錢 詳見下圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7iFo9k4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7iFo9k4.jpg&h=45e611f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/104845_3363e4070c88e5fd855f9b4fe515e7d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F104845_3363e4070c88e5fd855f9b4fe515e7d4.jpg&h=b9c6054d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拎左車 去左沙灘睇左陣女 之後入黑後去搵野食<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/105027_570081ee0cce0731308df2e0f753825c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F105027_570081ee0cce0731308df2e0f753825c.jpg&h=32ec8d6a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/105031_2bec2388f257d10acbb859e5c456f2ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F105031_2bec2388f257d10acbb859e5c456f2ac.jpg&h=982fdd4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zs9NZ31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZs9NZ31.jpg&h=5aef329d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e63a5659329064a44d98d7f9e910fd69076e5c04","tid":149650,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T02:59:06.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5日4夜係咪夠玩？？"},{"pid":"8ca12bf423659024ba63fe6d66ac0f8d811b2f6f","tid":149650,"uid":36391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T03:09:51.0