ttps://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/161238_e68f7d5caf1225714e8c0d806daed374.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F161238_e68f7d5caf1225714e8c0d806daed374.jpg&h=e049f2f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CEV5G86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCEV5G86.jpg&h=e8927811&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/161244_c91deafd666595c0ae498ceaeb49bdcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F161244_c91deafd666595c0ae498ceaeb49bdcf.jpg&h=4aeda300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過個夜市好冷清 無咩鋪頭開 好彩咁岩去到人表演傳統舞步 如果唔係都幾無悶<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/161552_6d46c1d3a0d2a3868fd8a72dbd0c1100.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F161552_6d46c1d3a0d2a3868fd8a72dbd0c1100.jpg&h=93233563&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/161555_667081d8ab1c6e4e4428990557bfb21d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F161555_667081d8ab1c6e4e4428990557bfb21d.jpg&h=7a24104d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/161559_8956fc033816df9d4bd4ad0ee5155ff0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F161559_8956fc033816df9d4bd4ad0ee5155ff0.jpg&h=78bd3eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反而野食都唔錯 唔算好貴依餐 20usd 兩個人<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/162053_82774c8f33e276c333a0e5de7b441ac7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F162053_82774c8f33e276c333a0e5de7b441ac7.jpg&h=2fcd3f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/162056_19606927001d