/i/4kVLpku.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4kVLpku.jpg&h=cd256b5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會係到跳水 唔少人一家大細揸車過黎野餐 家庭樂 再行遠少少 黎到最後一站 海盗餐廳 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/15/105220_42a5b5ba7392b393eae21b1297605970.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F15%2F105220_42a5b5ba7392b393eae21b1297605970.jpg&h=8aa517e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/15/105221_017de2c0e20ffdf77bdcca2f185b3601.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F15%2F105221_017de2c0e20ffdf77bdcca2f185b3601.jpg&h=a84065b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叫左個BBQ COMBO 大約16usd 味道唔錯 <br />\n配埋個靚景 真係好寫意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/15/105221_43881287f7973f7264aa44c8cb39358b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F15%2F105221_43881287f7973f7264aa44c8cb39358b.jpg&h=4a1f2c14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a1BgpGd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa1BgpGd.jpg&h=232f01ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50hmrH3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50hmrH3.jpg&h=541812c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5eb39966e67139a08cb22e96e539359b593bd445","tid":149650,"uid":90258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:12:53.000Z","msg":"C兄，請問邊間租車呀？<br />\n黎緊5月去<br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"59e625007ede5cb8470cdbba45f4250c164701d6","tid":149650,"uid":21992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:12:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>C兄，請問邊間租車呀？<br />\n黎緊5月去<br />\nThanks</blockquote><br />\nDollar 樂達 機場拎還車加20usd"},